<p>Firmly focused on Rails deployment, we grew rapidly in popularity, hosting fully managed apps for large companies such as Amnesty International, Channel4, MTV and many more.</p>

<p>In 2010, we began work on a whole new platform built from the ground up. After almost 18 months of development, Brightbox Cloud was launched in September 2011.</p>;	"ü<!DOCTYPE html>
