<div class="grid_9">
<p>We provide a very easy-to-use <a href="http://docs.brightbox.com/guides/cli/getting-started.html">command-line interface</a> (CLI) which interacts with our <a href="https://api.gb1.brightbox.com/1.0/">RESTful API</a>.</p>

<p>There are also higher level <a href="http://docs.brightbox.com/references/api.html">Ruby and Python libraries</a> available to get you started quickly.</p>

<p>Our flexible OAuth-based authentication system gives you fine grained control over who or what has access to your account and resources via the API.</p>
</div>

