      <h2>Overview</h2>
    
      <p>Brightbox is made up of developers and engineers and we build things that we want to use. We‚Äôre obsessive about great user experience and passionate about high availability, performance and consistency, (though not all at once ;)</p>

<p>We take our work seriously but we have a lot of fun.</p>

<p>Like our systems, our teams are geographically distributed, communicating in real-time throughout the working day. We‚Äôre a lean organisation, no middle managers or pointy haired bosses. Our development, engineering and operations teams all work closely together which shortens the feedback loop and means we get things done better.</p>

<p>We support our community by sponsoring events, or by <a href='https://github.com/brightbox'>contributing to free software projects</a>.</p>
      
