"3<%= render "blog_archive", @item.attributes %>;@•",/static/images/bg/noise_light_grey.png/{;{␀"/about/jobs/{;{	;"?<p>We don‚Äôt have any specific vacancies at the moment but we‚Äôre always on the look out for outstanding sysadmins, Ruby developers and support staff to expand our team. Some job descriptions are below to help give you an idea of what we‚Äôre looking for.</p>

<p>If you think you&#8217;re suitable, send a hello email, and a CV to <a href='mailto:jobs@brightbox.co.uk'>jobs@brightbox.co.uk</a>. Your CV should be in an open format, preferably PDF or plain text.</p>

<p>As always, recruitment agents should e-mail our special recruitment company email address: <a href='mailto:root@localhost'>root@localhost</a>.</p>

<p>Recruitment agents, as some of you don&#8217;t get the hint: we never consider candidates from recruitment agents. Please leave us alone.</p>

<h3 id='linux_systems_administrators'>Linux Systems Administrators</h3>

<ul>
<li>
<p>Work under the Technical Director and with our other systems admins to manage:</p>

<ul>
<li>our virtual hosting platform</li>

<li>our MySQL and PostgreSQL systems</li>

<li>our networking infrastructure</li>

<li>our backup systems</li>

<li>our monitoring systems expansion</li>
</ul>
</li>

<li>
<p>Provide customer service and support</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>Participate in an out-of-hours emergency on-call rota</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>Work from home or our office in Leeds</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>Occasional visits to our hosting data centres for new builds and hardware maintenance</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>Update technical and process documentation</p>
</li>
</ul>

<h4 id='qualifications'>Qualifications</h4>

<ul>
<li>2+ years experience with GNU/Linux based systems / 5+ years for a senior role</li>

<li>Experience with web technologies such as NGINX, Apache, HAproxy</li>

<li>Experience with Ruby, Rails desirable</li>

<li>Familiarity with Puppet, Virtualization, MySQL, PostgreSQL, LVM desirable</li>

<li>Familiarity with common Internet services such as DNS and SMTP</li>

<li>Experience working with customers</li>

<li>Ability to work both independently and as part of a team</li>

<li>Keeps up with new technologies and developments</li>

<li>Project management experience for Senior Sysadmins</li>

<li>Good written and verbal communication skills</li>
</ul>

<h3 id='ruby_developerssenior_developers'>Ruby Developers/Senior Developers</h3>

<p>Work under the Senior Ruby Software Engineer and with our other developers to:</p>

<ul>
<li>Maintain and extend our cloud management systems</li>

<li>Maintain and extend our billing systems</li>

<li>Work on side-projects that help the community and promote Brightbox</li>

<li>Extract code to be shared with the community as open source/free software</li>

<li>Invent and develop new ideas for services and products</li>

<li>Senior Developers would also be expected to manage several concurrent projects</li>

<li>Work from home or our office in Leeds</li>
</ul>

