    <h2>Command Line Interface Reference</h2>
    
    <p>The Brightbox CLI is a command line interface to create and manage Servers via the Brightbox Cloud API. It needs to be configured with your API client id and secret.</p>

<ul>
<li><a href='/guides/cli/installation.html'>Installing the CLI</a></li>

<li><a href='cli/configuration.html'>CLI Configuration</a></li>

<li><a href='cli/servers.html'>Managing Servers</a></li>

<li><a href='cli/development.html'>CLI development</a></li>
</ul>
