"3<%= render "blog_archive", @item.attributes %>;@–"//static/fonts/InfoTextWebPro-Semibold.eot/{;{␀"/{;{	;"u<p>Here you can find the documentation for the new <a href='http://beta.brightbox.com'>Brightbox Cloud platform</a>. The Brightbox Cloud is currently in beta and this documentation is still being written, but it&#8217;s a good starting point.</p>

<h4 id='getting_started'><a href='/guides/cli/getting-started.html'>Getting Started</a></h4>

<p>A step-by-step guide to getting up and running quickly</p>

<h4 id='guides_and_howtos'><a href='/guides'>Guides and Howtos</a></h4>

<p>All step by step guides on how to use various features.</p>

