<p>Load Balancers are billed by the hour, to an accuracy of one minute<sup>1</sup>. Internet data in and out of Load Balancers is billed at the [normal price](#data). Each Load Balancer is highly available within a Region - designed to tolerate the loss of an entire Zone. Each Load Balancer supports multiple protocols.</p>

<p>Currently, each Load Balancer is able to comfortably handle 5,000 concurrent connections. Soon, additional scaling options will be available to handle even larger numbers of concurrent connections.</p>

<p class='footnote'><sup>1</sup> Load Balancers are billed for a minimum of 1 hour for the first hour, and per-minute accuracy thereafter (read <a href='#hour_minimum' class='highlight'>why?</a>)</p>
