<h2 id='debugging_the_cli'>Debugging the CLI</h2>

<p>The Command Line Interface tools will output debugging information if you set the DEBUG environment variable to 1. If you come across a bug, try rerunning the command with this set and send the output to us along with the report. Thanks!</p>

<pre><code>$ DEBUG=1 brightbox-servers explode</code></pre>;	"#<!DOCTYPE html>
