<h3 id='how_do_i_resize_my_server'>How do I resize my server?</h3>

<p>We don&#8217;t support resizing in-place. You need to <a href='/guides/cli/create-a-snapshot.html'>snapshot your server</a> and create a new one using the snapshot. You&#8217;ll need to shrink the filesystem and partition if you want to resize to a smaller disk.</p>;	"í<!DOCTYPE html>
