id         owner      type      created_on  status  size   name
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
img-1okdf  brightbox  official  2010-11-19  public  20480  FreeBSD 8.1 minimal (i686)
img-aoubd  brightbox  official  2010-11-19  public  20480  FreeBSD 8.1 minimal (x86_64)
