      <h2>Solutions</h2>

      <p class="intro">This section will be devoted to showing how customers can make use of Brightbox products in their business.</p>

      <p>Each individual &#8220;solution&#8221; page will follow similar pattern&#8230;</p>

<ul>
<li>Clear benefit statement and nice big relevant image</li>

<li>Several paragraphs of text with any relevant diagrams (demonstrate deep knowledge of included target customer segments i.e. needs/wants)</li>

<li>Describe and link to relevant products and features (e.g Cloud balancers)</li>

<li>List benefits that Brightbox can offer through above products/features)</li>

<li>Related links (e.g case studies, partner programmes, blog posts, external links, howtos)</li>

<li>(later) downloadable ‚ÄúSolution‚Äù white paper w/case studies ‚óè Call to action * Q&amp;As</li>
</ul>

<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer ac posuere dolor. Donec consectetur rhoncus porta. Praesent vulputate interdum tempor. Pellentesque et arcu a libero congue sodales. Donec nunc erat, ullamcorper et congue quis, adipiscing vel massa. Proin a dui libero, ut mattis diam. Etiam eros metus, rhoncus nec adipiscing eget, vulputate id leo. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque dui neque, commodo sed accumsan quis, porttitor in turpis. Aenean suscipit tellus vel ligula lacinia pharetra. Sed sit amet dui id ante bibendum malesuada in eget eros. Maecenas eget massa metus.</p>
<hr /><div class='grid_8 push_1 alpha'>
<h3>By sector:</h3>

<ul>
<li>for Developers</li>

<li>for Ecommerce</li>

<li>for Startups</li>

<li>for Social media &amp; gaming</li>

<li>for Education</li>

<li>for SMB/SMEs</li>

<li>for Enterprises</li>

