* Clear benefit statement and nice big relevant image
* Several paragraphs of text with any relevant diagrams (demonstrate deep knowledge of included target customer segments i.e. needs/wants)
* Describe and link to relevant products and features (e.g Cloud balancers)
* List benefits that Brightbox can offer through above products/features)
* Related links (e.g case studies, partner programmes, blog posts, external links, howtos)
