<p>If you encounter a problem with our systems, then make sure to check our <strong><a href='http://status.gb1.brightbox.com'>status page</a></strong> which tracks any current issues and will contain details of what is wrong and when we expect it to be fixed.</p>

<h3>Report a problem</h3>

<p>If you&#8217;ve checked the <strong><a href='http://status.gb1.brightbox.com'>status page</a></strong> and are sure you&#8217;re experiencing an unreported problem, you should contact our support team by emailing <a href='mailto:support@brightbox.com'>support@brightbox.com</a>. Please include:</p>

